{
  "text": "There is yet another case where rules can be provided: when there is a class \"Organism\", which is the union of two classes -\"Heart\" and \"Blood\" (there are relations \"part of\" between the classes \"Heart\" and \"Organism\" as well as \"Blood\" and \"Organism\" [CITATION_1] . The rule can be generated as follows:",
